安裝各式套件

建立一個function叫做pttTestFunction

此功能之中包含了設定要爬蟲的網址、建立表格、刪掉表格前十行(因為PTT前十行並非文章)、創立另一個叫做getContent的爬文的function、再用sapply重複getContent這個動作

pttTestFunction <- function(URL, filename)
{
  URL   = "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Baseball/index.html"
  html  = read_html(URL)
  title = html_nodes(html, "a")
  href  = html_attr(title, "href")
  data = data.frame(title = toUTF8(html_text(title)),
                       href = href)
  data = data[-c(1:10),]
  getContent <- function(x) {
    url  = paste0("https://www.ptt.cc", x)
    tag  = html_node(read_html(url), 'div#main-content.bbs-screen.bbs-content')
    text = toUTF8(html_text(tag))
  }
    allText = sapply(data$href, getContent)
  allText
  write.table(allText, filename) 
   
}

爬文、並將爬文內容寫進.txt檔

URL   = "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Baseball/index.html"
html  = read_html(URL)
title = html_nodes(html, "a")
href  = html_attr(title, "href")

                     href = href)
data = data[-c(1:10),]
getContent <- function(x) {
  url  = paste0("https://www.ptt.cc", x)
  tag  = html_node(read_html(url), 'div#main-content.bbs-screen.bbs-content')
  text = toUTF8(html_text(tag))
}
allText = sapply(data$href, getContent)
write.table(allText, "mydata.txt")

將PTT棒球版的第5001頁到5035頁(最新)存成文字檔

運用之前寫的pttTestFunction，搭配mapply重複一樣的動作，將爬到的資料依照頁面存成文字檔

id = c(5001:5035)
URL = paste0("https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Baseball/index", id, ".html")
filename = paste0(id, ".txt")
pttTestFunction(URL[1], filename[1])
mapply(pttTestFunction, 
       URL = URL, filename = filename)

將檔案弄成corpus的形式，並且刪除會影響文字雲真實性的字、標點、數字和空白

filenames <- list.files(getwd(), pattern="*.txt")
files <- lapply(filenames, readLines)
docs <- Corpus(VectorSource(files))
toSpace <- content_transformer(function(x, pattern) {
  return (gsub(pattern, " ", x))
}
)
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "※")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "◆")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "‧")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "的")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "我")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "是")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "看板")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "作者")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "發信站")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "批踢踢實業坊")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "[a-zA-Z]")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "推")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "有")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "了")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "都")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "你")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "在")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "要")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "不")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "也")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "沒")
docs <- tm_map(docs, toSpace, "會")
docs <- tm_map(docs, removePunctuation)
docs <- tm_map(docs, removeNumbers)
docs <- tm_map(docs, stripWhitespace)

建立文字的數量統計表，創造文字雲

設定文字雲的顏色、文字數量的最大最小值、文字雲字的大小等等

mixseg = worker()
jieba_tokenizer=function(d){
  unlist(segment(d[[1]],mixseg))
}
seg = lapply(docs, jieba_tokenizer)
freqFrame = as.data.frame(table(unlist(seg)))

wordcloud(freqFrame$Var1,freqFrame$Freq,
          scale=c(5,0.1),min.freq=50,max.words=500,
          random.order=TRUE, random.color=FALSE, 
          rot.per=.1, colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2"),
          ordered.colors=FALSE,use.r.layout=FALSE,
          fixed.asp=TRUE)
